description: Finally, my love of Real Housewives is finally intersecting with my love for #Qanon and draining the swamp. Here, Real Housewife of Orange County, Kelly Dodd (a fav), posts a story to her followers who have criticized her during #covid19 #coronavirus She is currently dating Fox News Correspondent, Rick Levanthal. She ends the video by saying, “And everybody soon will see what is going to happen. I can’t say right now, but you’ll see in a few days. It’s going to be positive.” Curiouser and curiouser #mymaria777
